# 🚀 Day 75/90 – Send Data from Flutter to FastAPI (POST Request)

Congratulations on completing **Day 74**!

Yesterday, Flutter **received** data from the backend using a **GET** request.

Today, Flutter will **send** data to the backend using a **POST** request.

This is exactly how your Blood Report Analyzer will eventually send report information for processing.

